platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: This wholemeal hero just wants to be toasted.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: I Am Bread is a little like the childhood game Hot Lava: youre trying to reach objectives without touching the ground. The twist? Youre a piece of bread, and the surfaces youre flopping toward are ones you can toast yourself on. As you hop through kitchens and bathrooms, youll need to avoid icky stuff like dirty socks and dishwater thatll make you less edible. Between levels, you get snapshots of your homeowners mental state as he slowly realizes whats continually trashing his place. The whole experience is inexplicable and delightfully weird.
